@@TJvCharMap
<TITLEIMG TJvCharMap>
#JVCLInfo
<GROUP JVCL.GridsAndContent.Grids,JVCL.SelectAndChoose>
<FLAG Component>
Summary
  Use this component when you want to allow your user to choose a character in a grid displaying the
  current character set.
Description
  TJvCharMap is a grid component similar to the grid available in the CharMap utility included in
  Windows. TJvCharMap can display the characters from any font installed on the system.
  
  On Unicode enabled operating systems it can also display the Unicode characters as well as the
  Unicode subranges (with some limitations, see TJvCharMapRange.Filter for details).
  
  TJvCharMap inherits from TJvCustomCharMap and publish many of its properties but does not introduce
  any new behavior.

