@@TJvCustomCharMap.ShadowSize
Summary
  Determines the offset of the zoom panel's background shadow.
Description
  Use ShadowSize to set the top/left pixel offset of the shadow behind the zoom panel. Setting this
  value to 0, hides the shadow. The default value is 2 pixels.
See Also
